verse.lines:
{lang-eng}A moment's space without God
Creates in me a hell;
But when He sheds His love abroad,
What raptures do I feel!{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}We now but darkly thro' the glass
Behold the God we own;
Then shall we see Him face to face,
And know as we are known.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Then satan with his fiery darts
Shall us no more molest;
His arrows cannot reach our hearts
When we in glory rest.{/lang-eng}
